531
00:53:23,460 --> 00:53:27,980
Oh my, look at him! He looks so handsome!

532
00:53:27,980 --> 00:53:30,850
Aish!

533
00:53:48,520 --> 00:53:53,770
He's so crazy. He left and is walking around at this time of night?

534
00:53:59,320 --> 00:54:04,480
Is it today? The day when I get pay-back?

535
00:54:15,380 --> 00:54:17,320
Look forward to it,

536
00:54:18,980 --> 00:54:21,260
