537
00:54:24,350 --> 00:54:29,800
How is this feeling? You always put me in a headlock, what a sight!

538
00:54:46,300 --> 00:54:49,580
Isn't she your sister?

539
00:54:50,330 --> 00:54:51,630
What?

540
00:54:54,580 --> 00:54:56,110
