541
00:54:56,110 --> 00:55:00,540
What is this? Did Ban Ryu violate that girl?

542
00:55:00,540 --> 00:55:05,330
Is it okay for Hwarang to act that way? He just touched as he pleased!

543
00:55:05,970 --> 00:55:10,380
I-I did what?

544
00:55:10,380 --> 00:55:12,740
The truth is, you looked like him from behind...

545
00:55:12,740 --> 00:55:15,530
Hey! Come out!

546
00:55:20,510 --> 00:55:26,290
Ban Ryu! Ban Ryu! You! What did you do to my sister?!

547
00:55:28,970 --> 00:55:32,740
Tell me! What did this jerk do to you?!

548
00:55:32,740 --> 00:55:35,590
No, it's not that...

549
00:55:35,590 --> 00:55:39,340
You knew she was my sister, so you did this on purpose, didn't you?

550
00:55:39,340 --> 00:55:41,730
Hold it in, okay?

551
00:55:41,730 --> 00:55:44,100
Brother, the truth is—

552
00:55:44,100 --> 00:55:49,440
Don't speak. I'll handle everything, so stay still.

553
00:55:49,440 --> 00:55:54,250
Today, I am going to kill you.

554
00:56:08,780 --> 00:56:10,680
Oh! Aigo.

555
00:56:10,680 --> 00:56:12,860
Aigo.

556
00:56:14,010 --> 00:56:15,190
Sorry.

557
00:56:18,050 --> 00:56:20,110
Are you okay?

558
00:56:20,980 --> 00:56:23,260
Are you really okay?

559
00:56:30,470 --> 00:56:33,170
How did you get out?

560
00:56:34,040 --> 00:56:35,600
By climbing over the wall.

561
00:56:35,600 --> 00:56:39,880
