566
00:56:57,210 --> 00:56:59,260
Mother's birthday.

567
00:56:59,260 --> 00:57:03,940
♫  That path that I have found  ♫

568
00:57:03,940 --> 00:57:08,460
I don't know Mother's memorial day because we don't know when she passed away.

569
00:57:08,460 --> 00:57:12,350
♫  Like a dream  ♫

570
00:57:12,350 --> 00:57:16,300
Since you're here, I feel reassured.

571
00:57:16,300 --> 00:57:20,830
So whether you get in trouble or not, I don't want to think about that now.

572
00:57:20,830 --> 00:57:26,350
Right now, I just like that you're next to me.

