577
00:57:50,420 --> 00:57:54,550
What, why? Was Mother's lullaby nothing much?

578
00:57:54,550 --> 00:57:56,470
♫ I will never  ♫

579
00:57:56,470 --> 00:57:57,520
Brother.

580
00:57:57,520 --> 00:58:03,300
♫  I won't let you go. You're my everything.  ♫

